org.apache.poi.hpsf

Class DocumentSummaryInformation

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.poi.hpsf.PropertySet
      • org.apache.poi.hpsf.DocumentSummaryInformation

  • public class DocumentSummaryInformation
extends PropertySet
    Convenience class representing a DocumentSummary Information stream in a Microsoft Office document.(方便类，表示Microsoft Office文档中的Document摘要信息流。)
    See Also:
    SummaryInformation

        public DocumentSummaryInformation(PropertySet ps)
                           throws UnexpectedPropertySetTypeException
        Creates a DocumentSummaryInformation from a given PropertySet.(从给定的Property Set创建Document SummaryInfo。)
        Parameters:
        ps - A property set which should be created from a document summary information stream.(ps -应从文档摘要信息流创建的属性集。)
        Throws:
        UnexpectedPropertySetTypeException - if ps does not contain a document summary information stream.(UnexpectedPropertySetType异常-如果ps不包含文档摘要信息流。)

      • DocumentSummaryInformation

        public DocumentSummaryInformation(java.io.InputStream stream)
                           throws NoPropertySetStreamException,
                                  java.io.IOException
        Creates a DocumentSummaryInformation instance from an InputStream in the Horrible Property Set Format.

        The constructor reads the first few bytes from the stream and determines whether it is really a property set stream. If it is, it parses the rest of the stream. If it is not, it resets the stream to its beginning in order to let other components mess around with the data and throws an exception.

        (以可怕的属性集格式从InputStream创建DocumentSummaryInfo实例。构造函数从流中读取前几个字节并确定它是否真正是属性集流。如果是，它就会解析流的其余部分。如果不是，它会将流重置为开头，以便让其他组件处理数据并引发异常。)
        Parameters:
        stream - Holds the data making out the property set stream.(stream -保存构成属性集流的数据。)
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException - if the InputStream cannot be accessed as needed.(java.io. IOResponse-如果无法按需访问InputStream。)
        NoPropertySetStreamException - if the input stream does not contain a property set.(NoPropertySetStream异常-如果输入流不包含属性集。)

      • getApplicationVersion

        public int getApplicationVersion()
        Gets the version of the Application which wrote the Property set, stored with the two high order bytes having the major version number, and the two low order bytes the minor version number.

        This will be 0 if no version is set.

        (获取编写属性集的应用程序的版本，存储在具有主版本号的两个高位字节和具有次版本号的两个低位字节中。如果未设置版本，该值将为0。)
        Returns:
        the Application version(应用程序版本)

      • setApplicationVersion

        public void setApplicationVersion(int version)
        Sets the Application version, which must be a 4 byte int with the two high order bytes having the major version number, and the two low order bytes the minor version number.(设置应用程序版本，该版本必须是4字节int，其中两个高位字节具有主版本号，两个低位字节具有次版本号。)
        Parameters:
        version - the Application version(version -应用程序版本)

      • removeApplicationVersion

        public void removeApplicationVersion()
        Removes the Application Version(验证应用程序版本)
